properties.headline: Flood Advisory issued February 5 at 9:59PM CST until February 6 at 12:00PM CST by NWS Nashville TN
properties.description:
...The National Weather Service in Nashville has issued a Flood Advisory for the
following rivers in Middle Tennessee...

Wartrace Creek Near Wartrace affecting Bedford County

. Recent rainfall has caused area creeks and rivers to rise, and look to impact
the area over the next day or two.

The National Weather Service in Nashville has issued a
* Flood Advisory for
The Wartrace Creek Near Wartrace
* At 9 PM Wednesday the stage was 10.4 feet.
* Action stage is 9.0 feet.
* Flood stage is 14.0 feet.
* At 9.0 feet...Water begins to inundate Winette Ayers Park.
properties.instruction:
Stay tuned to NOAA weather radio or other local media for further information
from the National Weather Service.
